91
00:05:26,660 --> 00:05:27,911
Here come the deities.

92
00:05:28,870 --> 00:05:29,996
I got the chills.

93
00:05:35,752 --> 00:05:38,088
Your birth chart says you're very lonely.

94
00:05:38,171 --> 00:05:39,756
Mmm…

95
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:42,801
You're like a tree standing
at the top of a mountain,

96
00:05:42,884 --> 00:05:44,261
