don't stick around for long.

103
00:06:00,485 --> 00:06:03,989
People tend to come and go in your life
in 5-7 year cycles.

104
00:06:05,407 --> 00:06:06,408
Right.

105
00:06:09,035 --> 00:06:11,997
- She got divorced after about 5 years.
- Right.

106
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:14,124
- The ties didn't last.
- They were short-lived.

107
00:06:15,041 --> 00:06:16,459
However,

108
00:06:17,252 --> 00:06:19,462
when you do something physical,

109
00:06:19,546 --> 00:06:21,256
accidents and scandals

110
00:06:21,339 --> 00:06:23,258
come at the same time.

111
00:06:23,341 --> 00:06:26,761
Physical work just isn't your strength.

112
00:06:29,431 --> 00:06:31,099
Ah…

113
00:06:31,182 --> 00:06:33,435
That must be why
she ended up quitting sports.

114
00:06:33,518 --> 00:06:35,812
You're right. Her shoulder.

115
00:06:35,896 --> 00:06:37,105
That's why.

116
00:06:37,606 --> 00:06:38,732
This is too freaky.

117
00:06:40,483 --> 00:06:41,985
I was really surprised.

118
00:06:42,068 --> 00:06:43,862
Before I became a shaman,

119
00:06:44,446 --> 00:06:47,866
I was a competitive archer
from elementary school to university.

120
00:06:49,743 --> 00:06:51,328
I was pretty good,

121
00:06:52,162 --> 00:06:54,789
but I tore a tendon in my shoulder,

122
00:06:54,873 --> 00:06:56,541
and I couldn't shoot since.

123
00:06:56,625 --> 00:06:58,918
That's when I quit archery.

124
00:06:59,836 --> 00:07:03,632
I went on my knees, and cried
and prayed, saying I'd take this path.

125
00:07:08,678 --> 00:07:10,513
And well…

126
00:07:11,681 --> 00:07:13,975
