130
00:07:27,781 --> 00:07:31,409
They might approach you with affection.

131
00:07:33,828 --> 00:07:35,246
But they often get cut off.

132
00:07:35,330 --> 00:07:37,749
They keep being put to the test.

133
00:07:39,876 --> 00:07:41,127
Issues with men.

134
00:07:41,753 --> 00:07:43,213
