will come to nothing.

140
00:07:59,479 --> 00:08:01,481
It would be good for you
to keep that in mind.

141
00:08:05,443 --> 00:08:06,861
Okay, thank you.

142
00:08:10,323 --> 00:08:12,867
The fact that shamans,

143
00:08:12,951 --> 00:08:15,203
