that she's aware of all that.

163
00:09:12,635 --> 00:09:13,636
Exactly.

164
00:09:14,345 --> 00:09:16,056
- That's coming from her heart.
- Mmm…

165
00:09:19,851 --> 00:09:23,980
I feel terrible
to have to say this to you.

166
00:09:30,528 --> 00:09:32,572
But the child will become heavy later on.

167
00:09:33,448 --> 00:09:34,866
The child will become heavy.

168
00:09:34,949 --> 00:09:35,950
Huh?

169
00:09:37,118 --> 00:09:38,119
What does that mean?

170
00:09:40,330 --> 00:09:42,707
- It'll be too heavy?
- To overcome your fate

171
00:09:42,791 --> 00:09:45,627
