starting from when you get pregnant.

174
00:09:52,967 --> 00:09:55,053
When I said
the baby's fate would be heavy,

175
00:09:55,136 --> 00:09:59,599
I meant Lady Wish's shamanic gifts
will be passed down to her child.

176
00:09:59,682 --> 00:10:03,103
So as the mom, she will have to pray

177
00:10:03,186 --> 00:10:05,522
and work hard to change the baby's fate.

178
00:10:05,605 --> 00:10:07,857
If all goes well,
the child will turn out great.

179
00:10:07,941 --> 00:10:10,318
But if not, it won't get
to spread its wings.

180
00:10:10,944 --> 00:10:13,613
- Oh…
- If you were to be blessed

181
00:10:13,696 --> 00:10:17,408
to be given a child and give birth to it,

182
00:10:17,492 --> 00:10:19,994
you must hold tight to your Granny spirit.

183
00:10:20,078 --> 00:10:21,079
Okay.

184
00:10:24,249 --> 00:10:26,292
I'll do my best with the cleansing.

185
00:10:28,378 --> 00:10:30,255
You'll do great.

186
00:10:36,094 --> 00:10:37,637
That was a neat reading.

187
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:40,431
