189
00:10:42,934 --> 00:10:46,521
Young Master Plum Blossom
spoke calmly and very eloquently.

190
00:10:47,730 --> 00:10:51,025
- You studied engineering, right?
- Yes.

191
00:10:51,109 --> 00:10:53,111
You're the most well-spoken
engineering major I know.

192
00:10:53,194 --> 00:10:54,946
Ah…

193
00:10:55,029 --> 00:10:56,447
You're so good.

194
00:10:59,033 --> 00:11:02,120
Young Master Plum Blossom's
reading was so good.

195
00:11:02,203 --> 00:11:05,290
