- Ah…

200
00:11:34,736 --> 00:11:36,446
Gosh.

201
00:11:37,405 --> 00:11:39,782
Oh…

202
00:11:40,783 --> 00:11:42,243
Ah…

203
00:11:43,453 --> 00:11:44,704
Ah…

204
00:11:46,414 --> 00:11:48,625
This is what my deities say.

205
00:11:48,708 --> 00:11:50,376
Young Master Plum Blossom.

206
00:11:50,460 --> 00:11:53,838
My Grandpa and Granny spirits say
you couldn't be more pure.

207
00:11:53,922 --> 00:11:56,257
Your Granny spirit
is protecting you so very well,

208
00:11:56,341 --> 00:11:58,426
