209
00:11:58,509 --> 00:12:00,094
But my Granny spirit says,

210
00:12:00,178 --> 00:12:02,555
"Dear child,
you suffered because of the deities."

211
00:12:02,639 --> 00:12:05,725
- "You were sad, and you had a hard time."
- Ah…

212
00:12:05,808 --> 00:12:07,602
She talks fast.

213
00:12:07,685 --> 00:12:08,811
It's like she's rapping.

214
00:12:09,604 --> 00:12:13,483
"You're a shaman now,
and you were born to be one."

215
00:12:13,566 --> 00:12:16,527
"You started feeling the deities
when you were 3."

216
00:12:19,572 --> 00:12:21,115
- Wow.
- She's right.

217
00:12:21,199 --> 00:12:23,201
- That's right.
- She's right.

218
00:12:23,284 --> 00:12:25,203
2002, AGED 3, BECAME FRIENDS
WITH GHOSTS AND COMMUNICATED WITH THEM

219
00:12:26,996 --> 00:12:28,623
Here's something.

220
00:12:28,706 --> 00:12:31,042
When you were in middle or high school,

221
00:12:31,125 --> 00:12:33,336
