228
00:12:47,475 --> 00:12:50,353
2016, AGED 18
STARTED FEELING THE SPIRITS

229
00:12:52,188 --> 00:12:54,107
When I was in my last year of high school,

230
00:12:54,190 --> 00:12:56,276
