of COVID-19 complications.

241
00:13:31,978 --> 00:13:33,563
Oh, dear.

242
00:13:34,856 --> 00:13:37,233
Oh, no.
His aunt's not mentioned here, right?

243
00:13:38,818 --> 00:13:40,570
