or getting into an accident.

246
00:13:52,915 --> 00:13:56,502
Your duty now is to pray for
and console those who passed away.

247
00:13:56,586 --> 00:13:57,587
Okay.

248
00:13:59,756 --> 00:14:04,010
I sense an illness on your father's side.

249
00:14:04,093 --> 00:14:06,763
Was your father ill or something?

250
00:14:06,846 --> 00:14:07,847
Oh, my.

251
00:14:12,977 --> 00:14:15,021
His father was cursed with death.

252
00:14:15,104 --> 00:14:18,941
2016, AGED 18 - RITE TO LIFT
FATHER'S DEATH CURSE

253
00:14:19,025 --> 00:14:21,319
- My father's brothers were ill.
- Yes. Many people

254
00:14:21,402 --> 00:14:23,905
