366
00:19:51,774 --> 00:19:54,235
I couldn't keep up at first.

367
00:19:54,318 --> 00:19:56,278
My nickname is Rapper Wish.

368
00:19:57,279 --> 00:19:59,532
- She's known for it.
- MC Wish?

369
00:20:00,199 --> 00:20:01,951
Once I'm possessed,

370
00:20:02,034 --> 00:20:04,370
I start talking fast.
"Your grandfather blah, blah…"

371
00:20:04,453 --> 00:20:06,205
"That's why you run a business now."

372
00:20:06,288 --> 00:20:08,541
- Something like this.
- Ah!

373
00:20:08,624 --> 00:20:12,420
So, I tell my clients I'll say everything
quickly first and explain afterward.

374
00:20:12,503 --> 00:20:15,047
I talk first then go back
to the beginning.

375
00:20:15,131 --> 00:20:17,800
She talks that fast.

376
00:20:17,883 --> 00:20:20,886
- So that's her style.
- She's got rhythm.

377
00:20:20,970 --> 00:20:22,471
Skrrt!

378
00:20:23,639 --> 00:20:24,765
Fate Reapers.

379
00:20:25,307 --> 00:20:27,017
Between Lady Wish…

380
00:20:28,811 --> 00:20:30,521
…and Young Master Plum Blossom,

381
00:20:30,604 --> 00:20:32,732
