382
00:20:34,734 --> 00:20:36,610
This is so hard.

383
00:20:38,070 --> 00:20:40,448
What should I do? Why am I so torn?

384
00:20:41,615 --> 00:20:43,659
- I'll just follow my heart.
- Me too.

385
00:20:45,077 --> 00:20:46,829
If I were their client…

386
00:20:47,705 --> 00:20:48,998
They both did so well.

387
00:20:49,081 --> 00:20:51,459
It's hard this time.
They're neck-and-neck.

388
00:20:51,542 --> 00:20:53,377
How do you even choose who to eliminate?

389
00:20:53,461 --> 00:20:56,881
-I know. It'd be really hard.
-They're both incredibly good.

390
00:20:58,424 --> 00:21:00,593
- The Battle of Qi.
- Here goes.

391
00:21:00,676 --> 00:21:02,762
The winner of the 1-on-1 face-off is…

392
00:21:02,845 --> 00:21:03,929
Let's go.

393
00:21:04,847 --> 00:21:06,223
It's all about confidence.

394
00:21:06,307 --> 00:21:08,142
I was confident I'd win.

395
00:21:08,809 --> 00:21:12,021
I'm confident
I can hold my own against others,

396
00:21:12,813 --> 00:21:14,356
and I think I did an incredible job.

397
00:21:15,608 --> 00:21:16,776
They're so close.

398
00:21:16,859 --> 00:21:18,569
I don't know who will win.

399
00:21:21,238 --> 00:21:22,490
YOUNG MASTER PLUM BLOSSOM

400
00:21:22,573 --> 00:21:23,949
Gosh, look.

401
00:21:26,744 --> 00:21:27,745
Who is it?

402
00:21:29,705 --> 00:21:30,706
LADY WISH

403
00:21:31,874 --> 00:21:32,875
LADY WISH

404
00:21:39,465 --> 00:21:40,466
LADY WISH

405
00:21:40,549 --> 00:21:42,676
Lady Wish wins.

406
00:21:44,970 --> 00:21:46,514
LADY WISH SURVIVES

407
00:21:46,597 --> 00:21:47,723
Her experience won.

408
00:21:54,146 --> 00:21:56,232
- It's 3 to 2.
- Oh, 3 to 2.

409
00:21:56,774 --> 00:21:58,526
One person had the deciding vote.

410
00:21:58,609 --> 00:22:01,487
- It was close.
- It was incredibly close.

411
00:22:01,946 --> 00:22:03,239
It was a close match.

412
00:22:05,115 --> 00:22:07,827
It was 3 to 2. Really close.

413
00:22:08,911 --> 00:22:11,789
Well, I chose Lady Wish

414
00:22:12,373 --> 00:22:15,417
because she got

415
00:22:15,501 --> 00:22:16,836
his uncles' untimely deaths right.

416
00:22:16,919 --> 00:22:18,420
That was huge for me.

417
00:22:20,047 --> 00:22:22,466
This isn't something you can
do with your abilities as a human.

418
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:26,053
I must say what my deities tell me to say.

419
00:22:26,136 --> 00:22:28,264
I thank my Grandpa and Granny spirits.

420
00:22:28,347 --> 00:22:31,934
I'm pleased that I had a match
with a good person.

421
00:22:32,434 --> 00:22:34,478
I'm satisfied and content

422
00:22:34,562 --> 00:22:36,605
that I went against Lady Wish.

423
00:22:36,689 --> 00:22:39,859
If the match we had was

424
00:22:39,942 --> 00:22:42,611
a good one to watch

425
00:22:42,695 --> 00:22:45,739
and one where we were neck-and-neck,

426
00:22:45,823 --> 00:22:49,618
and if people will remember me

427
00:22:49,702 --> 00:22:51,829
for a long time after that,

428
00:22:51,912 --> 00:22:53,122
I have no regrets.

429
00:22:55,583 --> 00:22:57,501
Why did they have to pick each other?

430
00:22:57,585 --> 00:22:59,628
They were both so good.

431
00:23:01,714 --> 00:23:03,048
The Battle of Qi.

432
00:23:03,799 --> 00:23:05,467
The next face-off is

433
00:23:06,510 --> 00:23:07,511
