434
00:23:08,554 --> 00:23:11,056
and Meta Myungri Joon.

435
00:23:14,226 --> 00:23:16,186
Myungri
versus myungri.

436
00:23:16,270 --> 00:23:18,355
It's a saju face-off.

437
00:23:18,439 --> 00:23:20,149
Saju is a science.

438
00:23:20,816 --> 00:23:24,278
- Isn't saju great for guessing the past?
- Sure.

439
00:23:24,361 --> 00:23:27,197
They can tell you
what each decade of your life looks like.

440
00:23:27,281 --> 00:23:29,658
"Likely a scandal this year,
and an accident that year."

441
00:23:29,742 --> 00:23:32,411
It's about how
they put that together and interpret it.

442
00:23:32,494 --> 00:23:34,538
Saju is about who interprets it better.

443
00:23:34,622 --> 00:23:36,123
- That's right.
- Mmm.

444
00:23:36,624 --> 00:23:39,710
We interpret things differently.

445
00:23:39,793 --> 00:23:42,004
-You all have different styles, right?
-Yes.

446
00:23:42,087 --> 00:23:43,297
And different interpretations.

447
00:23:44,214 --> 00:23:46,008
They're both myungri experts.

448
00:23:46,091 --> 00:23:48,636
It's a battle of interpretations.

449
00:23:49,803 --> 00:23:53,182
I'll see how they do,
then make an appointment right away.

450
00:23:53,265 --> 00:23:54,892
- For a saju reading?
- Yes.

451
00:23:56,810 --> 00:23:59,146
Saju versus saju.
The battle of the century.

452
00:23:59,980 --> 00:24:02,358
One was an IT engineer.

453
00:24:03,192 --> 00:24:04,485
One used to be in finance.

454
00:24:04,568 --> 00:24:06,028
META MYUNGRI JOON
EX-FINANCIER SAJU EXPERT

455
00:24:06,111 --> 00:24:07,696
- IT and finance.
- Yes.

456
00:24:10,282 --> 00:24:13,285
I went to high school in the US.

457
00:24:14,912 --> 00:24:19,625
I worked in finance
in Washington, D.C. for a while.

458
00:24:19,708 --> 00:24:22,336
I was also in corporate finance

459
00:24:23,128 --> 00:24:25,214
at a firm in Yeouido.

460
00:24:25,297 --> 00:24:27,716
Then I started my own business.

461
00:24:27,800 --> 00:24:30,135
A myungri business.

462
00:24:30,761 --> 00:24:33,097
I look at my client's
date and time of birth,

463
00:24:33,180 --> 00:24:34,556
check their Great Luck Cycle,

464
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:36,558
then go into their Small Luck Cycle.

465
00:24:36,642 --> 00:24:39,186
That's how I can see
the flow of their life.

466
00:24:39,269 --> 00:24:40,980
BIG FLOW IN LIFE
THAT CHANGES EVERY 10 YEARS

467
00:24:42,022 --> 00:24:44,525
I used to work as an IT engineer

468
00:24:44,608 --> 00:24:47,027
before getting into myungri.

469
00:24:47,111 --> 00:24:50,572
There are 4 seasons
and 24 solar terms in a lunar year.

470
00:24:50,656 --> 00:24:53,033
I systemized the annual solar term data

471
00:24:53,117 --> 00:24:55,661
and developed my own theory.

472
00:24:55,744 --> 00:24:58,038
And I use that to read saju.

473
00:25:00,624 --> 00:25:01,834
There's no escaping this.

474
00:25:03,085 --> 00:25:04,420
This is

475
00:25:05,254 --> 00:25:07,256
an inevitable match.

476
00:25:07,339 --> 00:25:08,841
"I'll just do what I always do."

477
00:25:09,508 --> 00:25:10,718
I was confident.

478
00:25:12,428 --> 00:25:15,222
This is my specialty,
and my readings are very clear.

479
00:25:15,931 --> 00:25:17,599
I knew I could do well.

480
00:25:18,934 --> 00:25:22,271
They both brought out their tablet PCs.

481
00:25:22,354 --> 00:25:24,982
They're definitely different.

482
00:25:25,065 --> 00:25:27,693
Shamans were
ringing bells until just a minute ago.

483
00:25:27,776 --> 00:25:29,236
Now we have 2 tablet PCs.

484
00:25:29,611 --> 00:25:30,654
Because saju is about data.

485
00:25:32,614 --> 00:25:35,534
Meta Myungri Joon goes first.

486
00:25:36,368 --> 00:25:38,662
Pie goes second.

487
00:25:40,956 --> 00:25:44,543
Meta Myungri Joon seems
to have a stronger aura.

488
00:25:46,128 --> 00:25:47,713
Meta Myungri Joon,

489
00:25:48,297 --> 00:25:50,507
