490
00:25:51,008 --> 00:25:52,384
I wasn't nervous at all.

491
00:25:53,927 --> 00:25:56,597
Pie's fate based on his birth chart
was so very clear to me.

492
00:25:56,680 --> 00:25:59,433
I thought I had a good chance.
I wasn't really worried.

493
00:26:01,143 --> 00:26:05,064
As soon as I read your birth chart,

494
00:26:05,147 --> 00:26:07,024
I thought

495
00:26:07,608 --> 00:26:08,942
