496
00:26:13,072 --> 00:26:14,698
- What?
- A strong opening.

497
00:26:16,325 --> 00:26:17,576
"Fate of a beggar"?

498
00:26:18,118 --> 00:26:19,286
That's bold.

499
00:26:20,245 --> 00:26:23,415
No Wealth Stars,
Officer Stars, or Resource Stars.

500
00:26:23,499 --> 00:26:25,125
I see none in your birth chart.

501
00:26:25,209 --> 00:26:27,461
WEAK FORTUNE IN WEALTH, CAREER, STUDIES

502
00:26:27,544 --> 00:26:30,839
I haven't seen a birth chart like this
in a long time.

503
00:26:30,923 --> 00:26:33,175
I see maybe 5 of these a year.

504
00:26:35,177 --> 00:26:37,930
Those who study
classical myungri would say

505
00:26:38,013 --> 00:26:40,057
