506
00:26:40,140 --> 00:26:43,268
and you'd have a hard time making money.

507
00:26:43,352 --> 00:26:48,023
But I don't follow the classical theory.
I'm a modern myungri expert.

508
00:26:51,902 --> 00:26:54,446
This is how I interpret this birth chart.

509
00:26:54,530 --> 00:26:55,697
You're a late bloomer.

510
00:26:56,365 --> 00:26:57,699
A late bloomer.

511
00:26:59,409 --> 00:27:02,663
You're meant to succeed on your own.

512
00:27:04,039 --> 00:27:05,249
Is that why he quit his job?

513
00:27:06,416 --> 00:27:07,626
He's a self-made man.

514
00:27:07,709 --> 00:27:09,211
LEFT NEXON AND STARTED 'MYPIE'

515
00:27:09,294 --> 00:27:12,422
Now, your Great Luck Cycle
that started at age 14.

516
00:27:13,048 --> 00:27:15,509
You were very constrained then.

517
00:27:15,592 --> 00:27:18,345
You faced limitations.
It must've felt like you're pressed down.

518
00:27:18,428 --> 00:27:20,514
This is how I describe it.

519
00:27:21,431 --> 00:27:23,725
You're like a pressure cooker on the stove

