That's your fate.

891
00:48:23,901 --> 00:48:26,237
You must learn to accept that.

892
00:48:26,320 --> 00:48:29,573
It says here
that he had trouble making friends

893
00:48:29,657 --> 00:48:32,451
- because they never really understood him.
- Yes.

894
00:48:32,535 --> 00:48:34,161
