908
00:49:31,719 --> 00:49:33,137
Oh.

909
00:49:33,721 --> 00:49:34,930
Whoa.

910
00:49:35,014 --> 00:49:36,223
He's hitting back hard.

911
00:49:41,228 --> 00:49:42,563
One more thing.

912
00:49:43,397 --> 00:49:44,523
Don't belittle others.

913
00:49:47,818 --> 00:49:50,571
Noh Seulbi was too disrespectful.

914
00:49:51,655 --> 00:49:52,740
I gave her a warning

915
00:49:53,782 --> 00:49:55,075
