916
00:50:01,790 --> 00:50:03,209
Oh.

917
00:50:03,834 --> 00:50:04,835
So scary.

918
00:50:07,296 --> 00:50:09,298
- This is incredible.
- They're so fierce.

919
00:50:11,258 --> 00:50:12,343
I'm scared.

920
00:50:13,928 --> 00:50:14,929
Whoa.

921
00:50:17,014 --> 00:50:19,975
This is just how I give my readings,

922
00:50:20,518 --> 00:50:23,896
