928
00:50:39,161 --> 00:50:41,455
The thing in your chest.

929
00:50:41,539 --> 00:50:43,541
In your left chest.

930
00:50:47,795 --> 00:50:49,421
- Oh.
- Is that right?

931
00:50:49,505 --> 00:50:51,924
