Darn it.

947
00:51:47,771 --> 00:51:49,523
It's his death anniversary today.

948
00:51:52,693 --> 00:51:54,862
Oh, no.

949
00:52:01,744 --> 00:52:03,245
It's her dad's death anniversary.

950
00:52:04,705 --> 00:52:06,790
I had a feeling he was dead.

951
00:52:08,834 --> 00:52:11,170
Oh, dear…

952
00:52:14,173 --> 00:52:15,215
My dad…

953
00:52:16,383 --> 00:52:20,721
He really loved me, but…

954
00:52:22,973 --> 00:52:26,644
He was a man of many flaws.

955
00:52:29,521 --> 00:52:32,441
His love for me was a bit twisted.

956
00:52:37,321 --> 00:52:41,450
We weren't well-off when I was growing up,

957
00:52:42,242 --> 00:52:45,287
