958
00:52:45,871 --> 00:52:47,164
He went overboard.

959
00:52:47,247 --> 00:52:51,210
He was overly involved in my life
and was too possessive of me.

960
00:52:51,293 --> 00:52:55,714
That love sometimes
turned into obsession or violence.

961
00:52:56,924 --> 00:53:01,136
There was a time
when I mistakenly thought that was love.

962
00:53:02,596 --> 00:53:04,348
I hate him, but I miss him.

963
00:53:13,315 --> 00:53:14,650
I miss him.

964
00:53:15,275 --> 00:53:16,485
I'm sorry.

965
00:53:23,784 --> 00:53:25,119
