977
00:54:10,456 --> 00:54:13,083
- No one's strong.
- Absolutely. We're all soft.

978
00:54:13,709 --> 00:54:16,086
- We're all soft and squishy.
- Right.

979
00:54:17,880 --> 00:54:19,715
Maybe I am stronger than before.

980
00:54:21,341 --> 00:54:23,343
I think I just pretend to be tough.

981
00:54:24,887 --> 00:54:26,764
You said I had to, and you're right.

982
00:54:29,057 --> 00:54:33,020
Young Master Jiseon said
I had to become strong,

983
00:54:33,103 --> 00:54:35,397
