would grow up in abundance.

989
00:54:55,834 --> 00:54:57,794
I don't want my daughter

990
00:54:57,878 --> 00:55:01,590
or anyone else to see me being weak.

991
00:55:02,216 --> 00:55:04,885
I think that's why
I've pretended to be strong.

992
00:55:14,937 --> 00:55:19,233
Young Master Jiseon, Seulbi said

993
00:55:19,316 --> 00:55:23,612
-the deities saved your life.
-Yes.

994
00:55:23,695 --> 00:55:25,781
Do you agree with that?

995
00:55:25,864 --> 00:55:29,284
I was hit by a truck once.

996
00:55:29,785 --> 00:55:34,206
But I survived without a single scratch.

997
00:55:34,289 --> 00:55:35,290
Really?

998
00:55:37,709 --> 00:55:39,169
-You weren't hurt?
-No.

999
00:55:39,753 --> 00:55:40,754
My gosh.

1000
00:55:41,713 --> 00:55:43,632
Until this day, my mother…

1001
00:55:44,967 --> 00:55:45,968
Well…

1002
00:55:47,469 --> 00:55:50,556
She still can't throw away the sneakers
