1003
00:55:59,356 --> 00:56:00,357
Oh, my.

1004
00:56:02,901 --> 00:56:03,902
Hmm.

1005
00:56:04,528 --> 00:56:08,448
Looking back, I think that was
part of my spiritual calling.

1006
00:56:08,949 --> 00:56:11,827
It was when we were trying to avoid it.

1007
00:56:12,411 --> 00:56:15,038
