as if it were cut with a knife.

1018
00:56:42,774 --> 00:56:44,860
That meant the deities
were already with me.

1019
00:56:45,652 --> 00:56:48,405
My mother accepted my fate

1020
00:56:48,488 --> 00:56:50,282
