1021
00:56:52,534 --> 00:56:54,578
He's just like me.

1022
00:56:57,873 --> 00:56:59,166
Oh, dear.

1023
00:57:00,292 --> 00:57:02,419
Seulbi, what…

1024
00:57:03,545 --> 00:57:07,382
